Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,772)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  我可爱的金主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, me lovely paying--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.71,0:01:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,customers?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lunchtime
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Work day"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1398,250)}旧月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1410,726)}工作日
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.59,0:01:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still have a pulse
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽笛风琴音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calliope music?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我进恐怖片里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in a horror movie
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.23,0:01:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:31.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,208)}马戏团
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The circus?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得没客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wonder there aren't any customers
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又见面了  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello again, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驯兽师泥蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ringmaster Mudcrab?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准在我店门口停你家的小破马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't park your flea circus on my property
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我表亲身为市长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since my cousin is the mayor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给了我城建许可证批准我停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this city permit says I can
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你生意不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since you won't be busy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你一张马戏团的门票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here's a free ticket to the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你看看你的钱都跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can see where all your money went
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,务必要来尝尝我们这里的棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to try our cotton candy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你客人们都把这玩意当蟹黄堡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your customers are gobbling it up like it was Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  是马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, it's the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  每年那个驯兽师泥蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, every year that Ringmaster Mudcrab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都会来裤头村  偷走我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rolls into town and steals me customers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可今年他居然把他的破马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this year he's parked his shabby tent show
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接停我家店门前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right on me property
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去买个蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  改去那家马戏团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, let's go to the circus instead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然没活干  我先开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, since there's no work, I'll be going
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the circus?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.06,0:02:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破坏掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To destroy it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破坏掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To destroy it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破坏掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To destroy it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破坏掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To destroy it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not destroy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  过去嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said "enjoy"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去马戏团边看边嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to enjoy the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且老少皆宜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it'll be fun for all ages
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,票卖光了  全场又是座无虚席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got another sold-out show today, troupe
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家务必演得精彩  让观众绝对难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So let's give them a spectacle they'll never forget
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  观众绝对忘不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they'll never forget it, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不争气的废物员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And me own crew of incompetent misfits
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会把你马戏团变成笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will make such a mockery of your circus
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.37,0:03:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你一辈子没脸再回来裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you'll be drummed out of Bikini Bottom forever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我开门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up, I say
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs, I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are we dressed like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天马戏团里的人全病了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because everyone in the circus is sick today
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友驯兽师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my friend the ringmaster
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我们顶一下表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,asked us to take over the show
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新任驯兽师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the new ringmaster
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非得这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look great
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的悲情模样已经让我泪目了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pathos is already moving me to tears
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表演要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show's starting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请就位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Places, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位白痴们笨蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dummies and numbskulls
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老捣蛋鬼小捣蛋鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spoiled brats of all ages
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.92,0:04:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎观赏全世界最烂的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,welcome to the crummiest show on Earth
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dummies?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Numbskulls?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How rude
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肯定是那种嘴臭驯兽师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He must be one of those insult ringmasters
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样的话  好有搞笑效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, he's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's weird
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观众还挺喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They actually enjoyed that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着让他们看看第一出表演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, wait till they see this first act
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会让他们全讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gonna hate it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家看向我头顶上的钢丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call your attention to the high wire above me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.37,0:05:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请小丑海绵大废物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Introducing Sponge-O the Incompetent
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  是不是很不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, folks, isn't he appalling?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上退钱离场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave now for a full refund
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我掉网里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fall into the net already
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放海胆逼他掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Urchins should do it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.15,0:05:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下台了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会把我们都救出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get us out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟早会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eventually
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  大家都安静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, shut up, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请由我来指明出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to point out the exits
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为下一出表演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because this next act
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对会让大家大失所望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is sure to disappoint you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家不准掌声欢迎小丑章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't put your hands together for Squid-O
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界最伤心的小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the world's saddest clown
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观众不应该同情他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not supposed to sympathize with him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别对人家啊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't aw him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对他喝倒彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,台下观众智商太低  看啥都觉得好看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This idiot crowd is too easily entertained
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一出表演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got one last act
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对能让他们恨上这座马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that'll make them hate this circus
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体海熊  出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you sea bears, out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去去去去去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out, out, out, out, out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.00,0:08:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来这场烂得可怜又二流的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For our next pitiful, second-rate form of entertainment
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.63,0:08:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主角是训练无素的跳舞海熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have the mournful sight of a trained dancing sea bear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还是个假熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a total fraud
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到球上去  假熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get on the ball, fake bear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and dance
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他对假熊好凶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's being mean to the fake bear
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's finally working
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I agree
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这表演最烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This show is the worst
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I were you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就愤怒离场要求退钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd storm out and demand my money back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后拿着这钱去蟹堡王花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then go spend it at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your turn
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到球上去  驯兽师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the ball, Ringmaster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and dance
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.52,0:09:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到球上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the ball
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到球上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the ball
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.82,0:09:15.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:15.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get on
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  被迫上球跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I'm dragging
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要亲自去斗斗老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of Krabs myself
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪来的胆子  敢把我的马戏团变成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you turn my circus into a--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, a circus?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.27,0:09:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又哪来的胆子把我的蟹堡王变成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how dare you turn me restaurant into a
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人来的蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,empty restaurant?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你荡得走  但你躲不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can swing, but you can't hide
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你命悬一线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're hung out to dry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Urchins
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em off me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.30,0:10:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有我  你们什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd be nothing without me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你的壳炸个洞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna blast a hole right through your carapace
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老不死的戏子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you corny carny
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你牙齿全给崩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pound out all of your teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苍蝇馆子破老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you ridiculous restauranteur
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一周后
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你觉得蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, do you think Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会回蟹堡王来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will ever come back to the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概率不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在赚的钱比以前还要多不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's making more money now than he ever did
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家观赏你们眼前最壮观的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,behold the most incredible sight you'll ever see
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神奇无比  活力满满
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's amazing, and it's alive
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道能赚这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I knew I'd make this much money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老早以前就该拿自己当炮打你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd have cannonballed into you a long time ago
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love the circus
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界就数这个最赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the greatest dough on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.18,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFAF&}珊迪帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,368)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:51.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(574,440)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(724,662)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(746,532)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(582,538)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, sunshine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little doggie
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经历了这么多月以来的精密计算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After months of careful calculations
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.60,0:12:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的不合逻辑生物实验就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my bio-illogical experiment is almost done
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopping holes, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定要快过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to come quick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的闹钟坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My alarm clock is broken
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的闹钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your alarm clock, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定得要现在就去修闹钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we need to take care of that just now?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连插头都拔了  就是关不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even pulled out the plug, and I can't shut it off
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得动动脑子解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get my brain working on this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道问题在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see the problem
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, brain
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的海绵手指实在太过软萌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your spongy finger is just too darn soft and cute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按不动按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to press the switch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll fix it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要回去做实验了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just itching to get back to my experiment
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flying Dutchman?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just a painting
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm down here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么了  飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to you, Dutchy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都这样了还看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it look like?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个巫婆把我关进水晶球里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A witch trapped me inside a crystal ball
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我就全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I am in your hands
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try a little
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许再这么来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe some of this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快动脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, brain
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要用农场科技来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to use good old farm science on this one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我孵出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hatched me good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是很小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still tiny
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What gives, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰了  科研人员奇克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt, Science Officer Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底空间局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the Undersea Space Agency
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要你立刻前来协助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,needs your immediate assistance
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Dutchy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使命在召唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duty calls
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一颗巨大陨石正直冲地球飞来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A giant meteor is headed straight for Earth
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟往常一样  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and as usual, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有你才能拯救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're the only one that can save us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包在我身上  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can count on me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Earth
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得让开一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll need to scooch over a bit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏陨石又绕回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sidewinding stone is a-coming back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陨石不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad meteor, bad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet mother-of-pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于可以一个人安安静静做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally be all alone with my--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的实验成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My experiment worked
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's huge
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait right there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骑兵马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cavalry's coming
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是山核桃珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Pecan Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  山核桃珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Pecan Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是珊迪一号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Sandy Number One
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在实验室把你创造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I created you in my lab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你帮我做家务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to help me with all the chores
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,期间我整天都要出门在外解救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I'm out saving people all day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先从出去倒垃圾开始帮起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can start by taking out the garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山核桃珊迪讨厌出去倒垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pecan Sandy hates taking out the garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  山核桃珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Pecan Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不用出去倒垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to take out the garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你愿不愿意洗盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about washing the dishes?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.32,0:18:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山核桃珊迪不是你的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pecan Sandy is not your maid
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实验与预期完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This experiment is backfiring on me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想办法  想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to think, got to think
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的大脑累昏头了  想不动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bushwhacked brain is too fried to think
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  该来使出蛮力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, time to use some brawn
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能把事情放一放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm gonna need to pull the rip cord
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼叫紧急联系人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and call my emergency contact
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳  帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳  你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene, are you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简而言之  那个就是珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's Sandy in a nutshell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(724,920)}坚 果 壳 里
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也很想笑  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to laugh about it, too, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能快帮我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you get me out of here soon?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会快得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sooner than you think
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真心谢谢你  乡下姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly, country buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先盲猜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在实验室创造了个山核桃珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You created a Pecan Sandy in your lab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它突然发狂  你要我帮忙阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gone on a rampage, and you need my help to stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  差不多就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, that about covers it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me give it a think
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.69,0:20:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要打败山核桃珊迪只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to pummel pesky pecan into pie--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是上脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your feet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡做什么事你都上脚  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's your answer for everything, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I like it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三脚战术不错  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice triple footsie, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夸得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, ain't you sweet?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你的夹脚摔战术  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I liked your toe-jam slam, too, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈才没把我养成逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mama didn't raise no quitters
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把这腌椰菜桶的底细查个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting to the bottom of this pickle barrel
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要小心  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch it, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说说  山核桃珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Pecan Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山核桃珊迪会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pecan Sandy angry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.62,0:21:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为她创造我是想让我倒垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because she created me to take out her garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did what, now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.83,0:21:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我也会发狂的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heck, I'd go on a rampage, too
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What possessed you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那都是个馊主意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a bad idea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I admit it now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就理论上说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, on paper
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然事情经过我都了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that I know the whole story
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的山民智慧告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my hill-folk wisdom tells me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's only one way
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以解决山核桃珊迪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to crack this nutty problem
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要放了她  让她自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to let her loose to live her own life
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山核桃珊迪想要的  我全都要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want whatever Pecan Sandy wants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是山核桃珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Pecan Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想做什么就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And me do what me wants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎你随时回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all come back anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:03.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1546,648)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我们可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, we've earned a break
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.64,0:22:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me finally happy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, help us
